swiss consum price rise one pct in march swiss consum price rose one pct in the year to march , the same rise as in the year to februari , and against 0.9 pct in the year to march 1986 , the feder statist offic said . in march alon , price rose 0.1 pct after a 0.3 pct rise in februari . the march index , base 1982 , wa 109.7 against 109.5 in februari . the statist offic said the march increas reflect rise in certain sector such as food , cloth and household good and fall in transport , heat and light . both home produc and import good rose by 0.1 pct dure the month . but over the year as a whole , domest gener inflat reach 2.5 pct , offset by a 2.8 pct drop in import .